The Serial Adapater:

Adafruit USB to TTL Serial Cable - Debug / Console Cable for Raspberry Pi Product ID: 954
https://www.adafruit.com/product/954#technical-details


Folow the same steps for SerialToRasberryPi except for the physical connection.

------------
Connection:

Connect the wires to the J1 headers on your BeagleBone Green or Black as shown:
Note: pin 1 is nearist to the USB connector

Black wire to Pin 1
Green wire to Pin 4
White wire to Pin 5

